{
  "texts": [
    "\"Yes\"-The response includes clear next steps for the student. 2.",
    "\"To some extent\"-Some action is implied, but it is not clearly stated. 3.",
    "\"No\"-No action is suggested or the feedback ends the conversation.",
    "Each JSONL instance includes an instruction (as the user message), an input (composed of the full dialogue context and tutor response), and an output (gold label as assistant).",
    "This format enables effective supervised fine-tuning of Mathstral-7B-v0.1 on each dimension-specific classification task."
  ]
}